        "title": "feat(provider): add Morph Cloud direct SSH-lease provider",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add `morph` as a direct-only Linux SSH-lease provider with config and flag plumbing, provider registration, docs, and changelog/source-map updates\n- implement the Morph API client and backend for snapshot-based acquire, resolve, list, touch, release, shared-gateway SSH access, and provider-specific doctor checks\n- add backend, client, config, and smoke-test coverage, including the doctor wiring fix and config-backed Morph API key support in the live smoke harness\n\n## Testing\n- `go test -count=1 ./internal/cli ./internal/providers/...`\n- `go test -race ./...`\n- `go vet ./...`\n- `go build -trimpath -o bin/crabbox ./cmd/crabbox`\n- `scripts/check-docs.sh`\n- `node --test scripts/*.test.js`\n\n## Related issue\n- Closes #257\n",
